data.name: PB_SauceNao.ToolTip
data.value:
Search similar images with SauceNao. You can also use "F" key on keyboard. Ctrl+Click to set superior ID manually.
Image actions: Click on image to set your image as duplicate of it. Ctrl+Click on image to set your image as superior of it. Alt+Click on image to open that image in your default browser.
